    <section>
      <title>Fixed Bugs and Malfunctions</title>
      <list type="bulleted">
        <item>
          <p>Some missing files have been added:
            <c><![CDATA[~/include/edoc_doclet.hrl]]></c>, <c><![CDATA[~/priv/edoc.dtd]]></c>,
